data.name: NASOPHARYNGEAL AIRWAYS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Trumpet, Thickened and Slidable Types
- Highly Visible Size Indication along the Tubing

## PERFORMANCE
- Anatomic and Tip and consistent Hold allowing successful introduction
